Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.04,0:28:38.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,已经被洗脑了\N{\fs90}cars are bad, cars are bad, cars are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.72,0:28:40.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后当他们离开学校\N{\fs90}Then, when they do get out of school, after what--
