Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:12.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这就是他们从小到大看到的车\N{\fs90}Cos that's the car they grow up seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:14.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,还可能更糟 日产Juke\N{\fs90}Worse still, Nissan Juke.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.48,0:29:16.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你真的很讨厌Juke -是的 我讨厌它\N{\fs90}-You really hate the Juke. -No, I hate it.
