Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:21.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得它就不应该存在\N{\fs90}I object to it existing. It shouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:23.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,我厌恶它\N{\fs90}I loathe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.03,0:29:25.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,在高速公路上你会看到那两只愚蠢的\N{\fs90}On the motorway, you see them with their stupid,
