Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.72,0:29:45.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,我讨厌它们\N{\fs90}I hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.84,0:29:48.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在英国在售的最无聊的车是什么\N{\fs90}What's the most boring car on sale in Britain today?
