Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.63,0:29:51.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,棕色的阿斯顿马丁\N{\fs90}Brown Astons!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.38,0:29:55.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈哈哈 -刚刚谁说的\N{\fs90}Ha-ha-ha! Ha-ha-ha! - Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.11,0:29:59.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,出去 给我出去\N{\fs90}Get out. Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.89,0:30:07.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,保安 杀了他\N{\fs90}Security, kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:11.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,棕色阿斯顿个...\N{\fs90}"Brown Astons" my...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.13,0:30:12.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,听着 如果我是大众的老板\N{\fs90}I tell you what, if I were the boss of Volkswagen,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.35,0:30:14.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我会找到那个设计师\N{\fs90}I'd go and find the man who did...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.64,0:30:16.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,那辆很高的高尔夫叫什么来着\N{\fs90}What's that tall Golf called?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.50,0:30:18.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,那个 SV\N{\fs90}Oh, the SV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.39,0:30:20.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 SV 那辆专门给戴大礼帽的人\N{\fs90}SV, that's it. The one that's like a Golf,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.78,0:30:22.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,设计的高尔夫\N{\fs90}but for people who have stovepipe hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.26,0:30:25.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后用轮胎撬棍打死他\N{\fs90}And I would bludgeon him with a tyre iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.43,0:30:29.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做 这辆车没人会买\N{\fs90}"Why did you do that? Nobody wants one!"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.27,0:30:32.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,坦白说 我觉得大众正面临着更棘手的问题\N{\fs90}Just to be fair, I think VW have bigger concerns at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.86,0:30:34.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 接下来我要说说Oxford Ring Road\N{\fs90}OK, I want to talk about the Oxford Ring Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.11,0:30:38.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道离这里很远 大家也都看不见\N{\fs90}I know it's miles away from here and from anybody watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:40.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我想说的是 在过去两年内\N{\fs90}but the thing is, OK, for the last two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.07,0:30:43.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,这两个环岛一直在缩小\N{\fs90}they've been working on shrinking - slightly shrinking -
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.88,0:30:45.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,并增加了一些信号灯\N{\fs90}two roundabouts and putting some traffic lights up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.15,0:30:49.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,可你们知道这项工程的预算是多少吗\N{\fs90}Now, do you know how much the budget was for that job?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.86,0:30:51.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,呃 两个环形路口 就算一个一万\N{\fs90}Er... Two roundabouts, ten grand a roundabout.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.80,0:30:52.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,一共两万吧\N{\fs90}I'd say 20 grand overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.27,0:30:55.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,900万镑\N{\fs90}￡9 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.67,0:30:58.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,-真的吗 900万 -是的 900万\N{\fs90}-Million? Nine million? -Nine million.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.14,0:31:01.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们能想象承包商知道消息后脸上的表情吗\N{\fs90}Can you imagine the builder's face when he came out of that meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.13,0:31:05.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们竟然要给我900万\N{\fs90}"They're gonna give me nine million quid
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.70,0:31:07.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,就为了缩小两个环岛\N{\fs90}to shrink a couple of roundabouts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.84,0:31:09.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他才用了两年的时间\N{\fs90}Well, that's why it's taken him two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.37,0:31:11.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,要让这项工程看起来像是900万的规模\N{\fs90}He had to make it look like nine million quid's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.26,0:31:13.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实很难\N{\fs90}"Really difficult."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.55,0:31:14.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,一点没骗人\N{\fs90}This is not a word of a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.89,0:31:18.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,900万镑 可以买2800平米的豪宅\N{\fs90}￡9 million will buy you a 30,000-square-foot house,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.92,0:31:19.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像这样\N{\fs90}OK, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.49,0:31:23.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,这才是900万镑的工程\N{\fs90}That is a nine-million-quid house to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.43,0:31:25.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以用那900万镑建一座这样的房子\N{\fs90}You can have that or two shaved roundabouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.64,0:31:26.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者两个环岛\N{\fs90}for your nine million quid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.36,0:31:28.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,不不不 不是的\N{\fs90}No. No, actually. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.19,0:31:30.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 我说的都是实话\N{\fs90}Because - and this, again, is not a word of a lie -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.98,0:31:32.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,几个月前 这项目承包商\N{\fs90}a few months ago, builder man -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.02,0:31:34.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,我估计他是跟别人打赌了\N{\fs90}and it must have been a bet -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.84,0:31:37.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,他回到了议会 然后说\N{\fs90}he went back to the council and he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:39.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还需要一百万镑\N{\fs90}"I need another million quid."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.50,0:31:40.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,议会给他了吗\N{\fs90}And they paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.54,0:31:42.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,给了 竟然真的给了\N{\fs90}And they paid! They paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.47,0:31:45.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,没准他是这么说的 我把铲子弄坏了\N{\fs90}He probably shuffled in. "I broke me spade."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.18,0:31:49.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,能再给我一百万吗 没问题 乐意效劳\N{\fs90}"Another million?" "Yes, of course. Happy to."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.09,0:31:52.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能再说两句宝马吗\N{\fs90}Can I be cross for a moment with BMW?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.62,0:31:53.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都拦不住你 说吧\N{\fs90}It'll be difficult to stop you. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.11,0:31:56.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,是这样 宝马在去年公布了这辆车\N{\fs90}The thing was, last year they introduced this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.94,0:31:58.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们放出了图片 然后说 看呐\N{\fs90}They showed... They went, "Look at that."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.35,0:32:00.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家的反应都是 太棒了\N{\fs90}And everybody went, "That is fantastic!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.67,0:32:04.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一辆向1972年CSL Batmobile致敬的车\N{\fs90}It's an homage to the old CSL Batmobile from '72.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.01,0:32:06.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家都在问 什么时候开始造\N{\fs90}Everyone was going, "When will you make it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.79,0:32:09.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝马说不造 就是让你们看我们多厉害\N{\fs90}"We're not. It's just to show you what we could make."
