Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.59,0:32:12.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,-别这么吊人胃口 -说得没错\N{\fs90}- Just don't do that! - Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.72,0:32:13.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,实际上那个并不重要\N{\fs90}Actually, no, it doesn't matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.56,0:32:15.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为他们之后又发布了这个\N{\fs90}because they've come up with something else instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.05,0:32:17.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们看 这辆车是用来向\N{\fs90}This look. This is actually an homage
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.61,0:32:20.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,左边那辆宝马2002致敬的\N{\fs90}to the original 2002, which is the old car on the left,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.38,0:32:23.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得这车看上去简直美极了\N{\fs90}and that, I think, actually looks pretty fab.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.47,0:32:25.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-确实是 他们会造出来吗 -不会\N{\fs90}-It does. Are they gonna make it? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.41,0:32:27.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,那为什么要给我们看\N{\fs90}Well, why show it to us, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.37,0:32:28.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧我们能造这么好的车 但就是不造\N{\fs90}"Look what we could make but we're not."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.62,0:32:31.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,幸好宝马不负责紧急救援\N{\fs90}It's a good job BMW don't run the emergency services, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.80,0:32:35.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,看呐 你从那海岸漂过来挺远了吧\N{\fs90}"Oh, look! You have drifted a long way from shore there, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.50,0:32:37.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以用快艇拉着你走\N{\fs90}We could drag you back behind our speedboat."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.91,0:32:41.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你们会吗 -不 就是告诉你我们能这么干\N{\fs90}"Will you?" "No. No, we just wanted you to know that we could."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.50,0:32:43.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝马就是在戏屌\N{\fs90}What they're being is prick-teasers.
