Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.03,0:32:47.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不能说那个词\N{\fs90}I don't think you can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.38,0:32:49.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也觉得你不能这么说\N{\fs90}I'm not sure you can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.41,0:32:50.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,你能说戏屌吗？\N{\fs90}Can you say "prick-tease"?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.64,0:32:52.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,-耍鸡 -现在不让这么说了吗\N{\fs90}- A cock-tease! - Is it allowed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.99,0:32:55.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,耍鸡也一样啊 你只是换了个词\N{\fs90}"Cock-tease"? That's no different. You've just changed the name!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.78,0:32:58.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,只不过是说屌的不同方式\N{\fs90}It's a different way of saying "prick" or "dick".
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.33,0:33:00.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,那还可以直接说玩茎 都一样\N{\fs90}You could have said "penis tease". It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.78,0:33:02.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,唠嗑街开始变得有点污了\N{\fs90}Conversation Street's taken a really bad turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.20,0:33:06.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,重点是我觉得宝马不应该再这样了\N{\fs90}The point I'm trying to make is BMW must stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.69,0:33:10.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管 不管这是什么\N{\fs90}Whatever... Whatever it was.
