Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.39,0:33:17.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道第一个应该颁给谁\N{\fs90}I know who the first recipient would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.40,0:33:20.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们那天听到了这个惊人的故事\N{\fs90}Cos we heard this amazing story the other day.
