Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.88,0:33:23.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,停在路边 把窗户涂黑\N{\fs90}Sit at the side of the road, blacked out windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.98,0:33:27.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,人民公仆坐在里面看黄片\N{\fs90}civil servant sitting inside watching YouPorn. OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.42,0:33:30.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,本来就是 等着有人超速\N{\fs90}That's what it is. Waiting for someone to trip his camera.
