Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.82,0:33:37.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,把车牌摘了下来\N{\fs90}quietly undid its number plates
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.53,0:33:39.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,再装到自己的车上\N{\fs90}put them on his own car
