Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.05,0:33:45.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想说 这真是我听过的最有意思的事\N{\fs90}I mean... literally the funniest thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.85,0:33:46.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 先生\N{\fs90}Well done, you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.45,0:33:48.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了\N{\fs90}Top work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.92,0:33:50.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,-简直了 -我喜欢\N{\fs90}- Absolutely... - I love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.67,0:33:52.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,这件事干得真是太漂亮了\N{\fs90}That is top, top work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.75,0:33:54.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能说说阿尔法罗密欧的Quadrifoglio吗\N{\fs90}Can I talk about the Alfa Romeo Quadrifoglio?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.79,0:33:55.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不能 -为什么\N{\fs90}-No. -Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.73,0:33:57.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们该回归正题了\N{\fs90}Because we've got to get back to our film.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.62,0:34:00.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,今晚我们在意大利大壮游\N{\fs90}Tonight we are on a Grand Tour of Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.30,0:34:01.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯开着一辆劳斯莱斯\N{\fs90}There's James in a Rolls-Royce,
