Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.36,0:34:05.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开着一辆道奇地狱猫 以及两辆装满轮胎的卡车\N{\fs90}and me in a Dodge Hellcat with two trucks full of tyres
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.18,0:34:08.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我可以随时随地玩烧胎\N{\fs90}so I can do doughnuts whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.60,0:34:10.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 接下来的第二天\N{\fs90}Yes, and we pick up the action on day two
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.70,0:34:13.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,多亏了他 这趟路程\N{\fs90}of what was becoming, thanks to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.65,0:34:15.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,越来越见鬼了\N{\fs90}the journey from hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.93,0:34:24.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,当太阳在寂静且雾气朦胧的\N{\fs90}As the sun rose over the silent,
