Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.62,0:35:20.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,那些喜欢用安全带的人\N{\fs90}People who put their seatbelts on?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.18,0:35:22.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 穿脱安全带的人\N{\fs90}Exactly, people who put their seatbelts on and off
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.88,0:35:26.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,同时尽享人生自由与精妙\N{\fs90}and relish both freedom and sophistication.
