Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.96,0:35:29.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs90}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.99,0:35:31.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们能走了吗\N{\fs90}Can we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.12,0:35:32.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,你安全带系上了没有\N{\fs90}Have you got your seatbelt on?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.66,0:35:39.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们接着就出发了\N{\fs90}We then set off
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.94,0:35:43.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,同时决定对车进行更多的路测\N{\fs90}and decided to do a bit more road testing of our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.91,0:35:47.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我先说说阿斯顿马丁的内饰\N{\fs90}I began by talking about the Aston Martin's interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.14,0:35:52.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,优点是\N{\fs90}On the upside,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.18,0:35:56.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,阿斯顿马丁重编了奔驰的电子设备\N{\fs90}Aston Martin have reprogrammed the Mercedes electronics
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.05,0:36:01.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以提示警告音不那么 德系\N{\fs90}so the warning beeps and buzzers are now less...Germanic.
