Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.33,0:36:13.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,缺点是 其余的地方\N{\fs90}On the downside is everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.62,0:36:17.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,中控中间看上去就像\N{\fs90}Er... The centrepiece of this dashboard here looks like a...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.51,0:36:20.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢  像女性体征\N{\fs90}How can I put this?...like a lady part.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.21,0:36:23.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,至于门线这里 更是丑的可怕\N{\fs90}And then the door lining here, well, it's just hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.91,0:36:28.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像足球运动员的厨房台面\N{\fs90}It look like a footballer's...kitchen worktop.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.21,0:36:32.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,很烦人 阿斯顿这台车造得这么好\N{\fs90}It's annoying, cos Aston have done such a good job with the rest of this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.49,0:36:33.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我都惊呆了\N{\fs90}I was staggered
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.12,0:36:36.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,昨天它在赛道上的表现\N{\fs90}by how good it was at the track yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.68,0:36:40.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,而它就被这可怕的内饰拖累了\N{\fs90}And yet, they've let it all down with this ghastly interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.66,0:36:44.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,在地狱猫中 汉克 J 哈蒙德堡\N{\fs90}In the Hellcat, Hank J Hammondberger
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.72,0:36:47.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,并没有在意装配品质\N{\fs90}hadn't noticed the quality of the fixtures and fittings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.67,0:36:51.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是忙着捣鼓小玩意\N{\fs90}He was too busy playing with the toys.
