Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.64,0:36:56.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,计时器 仪表盘\N{\fs90}Timers, gauges...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.74,0:36:59.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs90}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.35,0:37:02.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的性能模式屏幕\N{\fs90}In my performance mode screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.19,0:37:04.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以测量 G力 刹车距离\N{\fs90}I can measure G-forces, braking distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.96,0:37:07.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,反应时间 四分之一英里计时\N{\fs90}reactions times, quarter-mile timer,
