Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.46,0:37:10.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fs90}It's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.98,0:37:13.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,无关紧要\N{\fs90}Irrelevant twaddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.80,0:37:17.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,无关紧要\N{\fs90}"Irrelevant twaddle."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.80,0:37:20.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我刚刚看见了我的平均油耗\N{\fs90}Oh, I've just seen my average MPG.
