Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.67,0:37:24.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,42.8\N{\fs90}6.6
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.81,0:37:28.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,百公里油耗42.8升\N{\fs90}Six miles to the gallon?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.54,0:37:31.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得这应该算胃口不错\N{\fs90}I like to think of it as a healthy appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.18,0:37:35.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯你的劳斯莱斯的油耗怎么样\N{\fs90}How many miles to the gallon has your Rolls-Royce been doing, James May?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.33,0:37:38.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,过去的48小时里是百公里18升\N{\fs90}15.7 in the last 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.58,0:37:42.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车是百公里13.5 升\N{\fs90}Mine's been doing 21 miles to the gallon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.83,0:37:45.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为它无聊 更因为它是棕色的\N{\fs90}That's cos it's boring and that's because it's brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.89,0:37:47.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,又来\N{\fs90}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.06,0:37:50.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,就这样 公路测试结束\N{\fs90}And, with that, the road test ended
