Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.38,0:38:07.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在另一座加油站见面了\N{\fs90}You join us at another petrol station.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.68,0:38:10.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是不要加油 但猜猜谁要\N{\fs90}I don't need any,but guess who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.07,0:38:12.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车给鸟类学家再好不过\N{\fs90}This car is excellent for ornithologists.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.72,0:38:15.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,这么驾驶太安静了 我听的到鸟的歌唱\N{\fs90}It's so quiet going along here, I can listen to the birdsong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.16,0:38:20.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}Hello, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.39,0:38:22.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢老天爷啊\N{\fs90}Oh, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.16,0:38:23.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,派对按钮\N{\fs90}Party button!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.70,0:38:27.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,别这么干了\N{\fs90}Stop doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.60,0:38:29.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,停\N{\fs90}Stop it!
