Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:44.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,很多烦人的里程过后\N{\fs90}Many frustrating miles later,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.26,0:38:46.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们来到壮游的下一个目的地\N{\fs90}we reached the next stop on our Grand Tour:
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.39,0:38:48.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,摩德纳地区\N{\fs90}the region around Modena,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.92,0:38:52.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,世上最伟大的三个车厂的家\N{\fs90}which is home to three of the world's greatest carmakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.03,0:38:58.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,当哈蒙德忙于\N{\fs90}And, while Hammond sped off
