Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.63,0:39:36.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,给来壮游的美国人画画赚了很多\N{\fs90}out of painting visiting Americans on the Grand Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:40.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,让他们看起来像是优雅\N{\fs90}and making them look like refined,
