Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.60,0:51:37.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,对它们冲着 噢\N{\fs90}Yeah, they're after his.. Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.14,0:51:40.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs90}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.43,0:51:43.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊天啊\N{\fs90}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.52,0:51:45.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们什么也做不了\N{\fs90}There's literally nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.22,0:51:46.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要背骂名了\N{\fs90}We're gonna get a reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.95,0:51:49.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是说他来不了 对吧\N{\fs90}Does that mean he's not coming on then?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.53,0:51:50.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,呃 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}Well, James...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.16,0:51:52.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,他掉了下去\N{\fs90}...he fell into the harbour,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.44,0:51:55.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,北海刺骨的海水正灌满他的肺\N{\fs90}and the icy North Sea waters are now filling his lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.30,0:51:57.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 他来不了了\N{\fs90}It's a no He's not coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.82,0:51:59.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦天啊\N{\fs90}Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.03,0:52:02.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧啊 我\N{\fs90}Well, look, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.26,0:52:06.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,我预料到会有这事发生\N{\fs90}-Oh -I anticipated something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.12,0:52:07.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是吗 -嗯\N{\fs90}-Did you? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.39,0:52:11.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我另有个填补时间的方法\N{\fs90}And so I prepared something else we can do to fill the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.80,0:52:14.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,是这样 你们知道\N{\fs90}It's this. You know Google have been
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.20,0:52:17.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,谷歌正在造无人车吧\N{\fs90}trying to build a self-driving car?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.12,0:52:18.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们造了七年\N{\fs90}For seven years they've been at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.73,0:52:19.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们这有张照片\N{\fs90}We've got a picture of it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.88,0:52:21.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,它看起来十分丑陋\N{\fs90}It's absolutely hideous.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.31,0:52:23.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我就想啊 这能有多难\N{\fs90}I was thinking, "Well, how hard can it be?"
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.52,0:52:25.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}- Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.15,0:52:27.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,十天前我就决定试一试\N{\fs90}Ten days ago I thought, "I'll give it a bash," okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.34,0:52:29.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我成功完成了\N{\fs90}And I've already finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.04,0:52:30.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是吗 -没错它就在这\N{\fs90}-Have you? -Yes, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.50,0:52:31.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是吗 -没错\N{\fs90}-Is it? -Yes, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.49,0:52:33.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我把它带进来 用手机控制哦\N{\fs90}Let's bring it out It's phone-operated.
