Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.77,0:52:39.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,前进\N{\fs90}Forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.03,0:52:40.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,别让北海的悲伤\N{\fs90}Please try not to be distracted
