Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.80,0:52:46.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,往前\N{\fs90}Straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.29,0:52:51.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,西蒙毫无生气的尸体\N{\fs90}...the harrowing scenes of Simon's lifeless corpsebeing fished
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.00,0:52:53.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,被钓出水面的悲伤一幕\N{\fs90}from the harbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.09,0:52:55.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道有些观众十分悲伤\N{\fs90}I know that's upsetting for some people.
