Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.13,0:53:10.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,鼓掌吧大伙\N{\fs90}-Cheer, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.49,0:53:13.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,左拐 左拐\N{\fs90}Left. Left. Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.87,0:53:16.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,看着真丑-往左 直走\N{\fs90}-It's hideous! -Left. Forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.40,0:53:19.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,-太丑了 等等\N{\fs90}-It's... So, hold on
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.58,0:53:21.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,-停\N{\fs90}-Stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.53,0:53:24.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,这一点都不天才 太丑了 真的\N{\fs90}It's not brilliant It's hideous, is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.04,0:53:25.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么能说它丑呢\N{\fs90}How can you say it's hideous?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.21,0:53:28.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可是原味山寨的谷歌设计\N{\fs90}I've copied Google's styling completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.01,0:53:30.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个化粪池吗\N{\fs90}Is that a septic tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.95,0:53:32.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs90}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.82,0:53:35.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,切了一半 然后扣上了这个躺椅\N{\fs90}Cut in half, and then I've mounted on the top this chaise longue,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.84,0:53:39.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以拥有者就可以舒舒服服的躺着了\N{\fs90}so the owner can recline in great comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.94,0:53:42.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,好好好 所以它到底怎么运作的\N{\fs90}Yeah, yeah How does it actually work?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.47,0:53:43.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,展示天才想法的时候到了\N{\fs90}Brilliantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.52,0:53:45.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,这下面有一个小摄像头\N{\fs90}Down here, a very small little camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.78,0:53:50.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,给内部系统采集路面信息\N{\fs90}That feeds a view of the road ahead to the system inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.56,0:53:51.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么系统\N{\fs90}-What system?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.54,0:53:52.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这儿有个引擎盖\N{\fs90}-Well, there's a bonnet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.52,0:53:55.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,来看看 准备好了吗\N{\fs90}Come round, I'll show you the... the gubbins. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.21,0:53:57.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,咳咳 这就是了\N{\fs90}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.42,0:53:59.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,啥 就是个人\N{\fs90}Well, it's just a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.81,0:54:01.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这儿只有个人\N{\fs90}-It's just a man in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.22,0:54:02.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,-并不是啊\N{\fs90}-It isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.61,0:54:04.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就是\N{\fs90}It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.92,0:54:09.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不不不 不是\N{\fs90}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.60,0:54:12.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,他不只是个人\N{\fs90}It's not just a man
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.96,0:54:14.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,他还是个罗马尼亚人\N{\fs90}This is a Romanian man.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.57,0:54:19.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在给祖国的新移民提供工作\N{\fs90}I am providing employment for newcomers to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.17,0:54:20.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,-天啊\N{\fs90}-Oh, God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.36,0:54:21.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你这话我就不爱听了\N{\fs90}-What do you mean, "Oh, God"?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.62,0:54:23.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,想想看 谷歌 嗯\N{\fs90}Think about it. Google, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.29,0:54:27.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,谷歌在让电子蚕食人们的饭碗\N{\fs90}Google, they use electronics to take away the work of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.61,0:54:30.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这个给他工作 让他体面生活\N{\fs90}This gives him a job, it gives him dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.59,0:54:31.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,-体面吗\N{\fs90}-Dignity?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.29,0:54:32.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-真的 很体面\N{\fs90}-Yes, dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.96,0:54:34.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,有点封建气息啊\N{\fs90}It's a bit feudal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.74,0:54:36.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,这明明是天才气息\N{\fs90}It's a bit brilliant is what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.22,0:54:37.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要关上引擎盖了\N{\fs90}Let me close the bonnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.63,0:54:39.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要开始处女航了\N{\fs90}I'm gonna go for my first-ever drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.27,0:54:41.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,首先上梯砸\N{\fs90}I'll go to t'foot of our stairs here,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.31,0:54:43.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个约克郡俗语\N{\fs90}which is a Yorkshire expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.32,0:54:46.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,厉害的是 上下车十分容易\N{\fs90}The great thing is, it's so easy to get in and out of, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.56,0:54:48.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,看到了没\N{\fs90}Look, there I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.80,0:54:52.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在可以不用手机 我可以用传声装置\N{\fs90}-Now I don't need the phone I can use my speaking tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.25,0:54:55.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊 这下面可藏着一个人啊\N{\fs90} -Oh, God!There's a man in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.96,0:54:57.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,罗马尼亚语的后退是什么来着\N{\fs90}What's Romanian for "backwards"?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.97,0:54:59.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,?napoi 应该是这个\N{\fs90}?napoi, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.70,0:55:02.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 还能双语控制\N{\fs90}?napoi. It is, obviously It's bilingual.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.20,0:55:03.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,太魔性了\N{\fs90}This is evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.76,0:55:06.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,谷歌都没做到的 我做到了\N{\fs90}Google hasn't made it work, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.57,0:55:08.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,倒 我还是说英语了\N{\fs90}?na... Backwards I'll just stick to English.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.82,0:55:11.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,倒 倒 倒\N{\fs90}Backwards. Backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.05,0:55:14.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,十分感谢\N{\fs90}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.35,0:55:17.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 这就是英国工程\N{\fs90}British engineering, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.79,0:55:19.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,和罗马尼亚零部件\N{\fs90}with Romanian parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.33,0:55:22.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,美妙的结合\N{\fs90}What a combination that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.06,0:55:25.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,擦 我的头\N{\fs90}Shit! Ah, my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.97,0:55:32.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,行吧行吧\N{\fs90}Yep. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.21,0:55:36.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我很高兴他走了\N{\fs90}-Anyway, I'm glad he's gone
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.39,0:55:37.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我也是\N{\fs90}-So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.08,0:55:40.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还十分开心的是接下来的内容\N{\fs90}No, I'm particularly glad because of what's coming up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.63,0:55:43.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊对对对 在之前的节目里\N{\fs90}Oh, yes! Yes. Now, right at the beginning of this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.52,0:55:46.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米在葡萄牙竞速中打赌\N{\fs90}Jeremy Clarkson said, when we were at a race track in Portugal -
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.95,0:55:48.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,是在广大观众面前说哦\N{\fs90}and he said it on the television -
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.99,0:55:51.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果他的迈凯伦P1\N{\fs90}that if his McLaren P1 wasn't faster
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.03,0:55:55.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,比哈蒙德的保时捷918和我的法拉利拉法慢\N{\fs90}than Hammond's Porsche 918 or my Ferrari The Ferrari,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.45,0:55:57.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以拆掉他的房子\N{\fs90}we could knock his house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.24,0:55:58.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,正如你所见 他失败了\N{\fs90}Well, it wasn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.94,0:56:01.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以趁杰里米不在家的周末\N{\fs90}so, one weekend when Jeremy was away,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.41,0:56:04.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们 放影片吧\N{\fs90}we...Well, roll the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.18,0:56:06.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是了\N{\fs90}This is it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.64,0:56:11.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,科茨沃尔德石材所建 200年历史的房子\N{\fs90}200 years old and built from beautiful Cotswold stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.54,0:56:13.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要说清楚\N{\fs90}Now, I want to make it absolutely clear
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.45,0:56:17.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是杰里米的房子 如假包换\N{\fs90}that this is Jeremy Clarkson's actual house.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.26,0:56:19.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 我以我孩子们的性命发誓\N{\fs90}Yeah, it really is I'd swear to my children's lives on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.81,0:56:20.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是杰里米的房子\N{\fs90}It's Jeremy's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.81,0:56:22.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,他爱这里的风景才买的\N{\fs90} He bought it when he fell in love with the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.69,0:56:24.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,这风景很漂亮\N{\fs90}It is a lovely view, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.59,0:56:26.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 现在我们可以除掉这碍眼的房子\N{\fs90}It is. It'll be even better soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.52,0:56:28.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,让这风景更上一层楼\N{\fs90}without a house in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.05,0:56:32.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的计划很简单\N{\fs90}Our plan was to smash the place down
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.64,0:56:35.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,用大家伙砸掉就行\N{\fs90}with some big demolition equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.19,0:56:37.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是有个问题\N{\fs90}But there was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.08,0:56:42.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,在这个地方\N{\fs90}In this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.60,0:56:44.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果政府发现蝙蝠居住在此的话\N{\fs90}you can't knock a house down
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.27,0:56:47.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就无法拆除房屋\N{\fs90}if the council find evidence of bats living in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.54,0:56:48.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这里有蝙蝠\N{\fs90}Well, they did,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.55,0:56:49.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们被要求\N{\fs90}and now we've been told
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.79,0:56:52.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,要先轻轻用手把屋顶掀了\N{\fs90}we've got to take the roof off, quietly and by hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.70,0:56:56.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,让蝙蝠有机会逃命\N{\fs90}to give the bats the chance to go and live elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.43,0:57:00.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 我发现现在只有我一个人在做这活\N{\fs90}James, I can't help but notice I am doing all of the work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.16,0:57:02.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,没办法 我不喜欢这工作\N{\fs90}Yeah, you're gonna have to. I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.77,0:57:06.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是个梯子 很简单只要爬上来就好啊\N{\fs90}It's just a ladder! It's a simple enough thing to operate. Climb it!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.81,0:57:08.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,你又不是我 一点都不简单\N{\fs90}Not if you're me, it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.24,0:57:09.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,这儿有多少蝙蝠\N{\fs90}How many bats are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.59,0:57:10.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,-一只\N{\fs90}-One
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.21,0:57:10.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就一只\N{\fs90}-One?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.75,0:57:12.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是 就一只\N{\fs90}-Yes, a bat
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.02,0:57:12.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就宰了它啊\N{\fs90}-Just kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.92,0:57:14.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,那我们会进监狱的 没门\N{\fs90}We'll go to prison, mate We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.58,0:57:17.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,就因为那长着翅膀的杂种老鼠\N{\fs90}Just because that little winged-mouse bastard
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.24,0:57:19.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,倒挂在这 还一脸得意\N{\fs90}is hanging upside down in there, feeling smug with himself
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.55,0:57:21.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我得爬上梯子 没法拆迁?\N{\fs90}cos I'm up this ladder, we can't knock the house down?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.73,0:57:24.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 上来吧\N{\fs90}We've got to do it, no choice, so get up here and get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.55,0:57:27.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德你知道我恐高\N{\fs90}Hammond, I hate.. I hate heights You know I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.67,0:57:30.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我讨厌梯子 我恨蝙蝠\N{\fs90}I hate ladders, I hate bats.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.06,0:57:32.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,几小时后\N{\fs90}Many hours later,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.84,0:57:35.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,蜘蛛侠并没来帮忙\N{\fs90}and with no help at all from Spider-Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.79,0:57:39.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于掀开了屋顶 蝙蝠可以飞走了\N{\fs90}the roof was finally off and the bat was free to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.70,0:57:41.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,但它会吗\N{\fs90}But would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.12,0:57:43.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,它为什么不飞去那边呢\N{\fs90}Why doesn't it go and live in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.20,0:57:45.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 讲道理啊 那对蝙蝠可是个好地方\N{\fs90}Because, let's be honest, that's perfect if you're a bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.61,0:57:49.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 可是它得乐意搬走啊\N{\fs90}Yeah, well, it might, but it's got to decide to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.67,0:57:51.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-能给它一点鼓励吗\N{\fs90}-Can we encourage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.83,0:57:53.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好吧 你可以在谷仓里\N{\fs90}-Yes, James.Why don't you go and stand in that barn
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.90,0:57:56.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,发出挑逗的叫声来吸引吧\N{\fs90}  and squeak in a sultry and erotic manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.27,0:58:01.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,那晚  蜘蛛侠侠站在谷仓里\N{\fs90}That night, Spider-Man stood in the barn,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.03,0:58:04.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,发出诱惑而挑逗的叫声\N{\fs90}squeaking in a sultry and erotic manner...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.53,0:58:09.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,蝙蝠也终于拜倒在了石榴裙下\N{\fs90}...and the bat eventually succumbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.84,0:58:13.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二天一早 我们终于可以拆迁了\N{\fs90}So, the next morning, we were ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.88,0:58:33.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这东西很有用啊 真给力\N{\fs90}This thing really works! This rocks!Oh, my word!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.44,0:58:36.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,如此这般 很快就可以搞定了\N{\fs90}At this rate, we'd be done and dusted in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.80,0:58:40.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 我的挑剔同事又添乱了\N{\fs90}However, my finickity colleague had an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.70,0:58:42.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德\N{\fs90}-Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.74,0:58:44.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,-干嘛 -停下\N{\fs90}-What?-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.22,0:58:45.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,-啥 -停\N{\fs90}-What?-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.54,0:58:47.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不能这样把它砸的粉碎\N{\fs90}You don't just smash it to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.50,0:58:49.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,应该分解它 让它齐整地倒下\N{\fs90}You're supposed to dismantle it and leave it in neat piles.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.06,0:58:52.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,务必要整齐地拆除 而不是砸碎\N{\fs90}It's got to be tidied up You can't leave it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.85,0:58:55.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,要是这么做 会完成的更快\N{\fs90}It's actually quicker if you do it methodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.18,0:58:57.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我去 只有你会说这种话\N{\fs90}Oh, God Only you would say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.54,0:59:00.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,整齐地拆除会更好 因为废墟更容易处理\N{\fs90}You want neat piles of bits that can be carted away.You need to work on that bit
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.02,0:59:02.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,应该这样做 从那部分开始\N{\fs90} and that bit to start with,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.72,0:59:03.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,剩下的部分会齐整地倒成一堆\N{\fs90}then the rest falls neatly into a heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.99,0:59:06.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是如何让这活变得如此无聊的\N{\fs90}How can you make even this boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.23,0:59:09.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不无聊 只是教你经验 我是过来人\N{\fs90}It's not boring. It's the way... I've watched it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.53,0:59:11.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,该这么做 不是砸碎它 我来吧\N{\fs90}That's how you do it You don't just smash it I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.28,0:59:15.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯抢走了我的机器\N{\fs90}James then commandeered my machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.78,0:59:19.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我带着新装备卷土重来\N{\fs90}so I got another one and carried on regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.74,0:59:28.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊哈 抓到了\N{\fs90}Ah! I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.36,0:59:37.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像在玩夹娃娃机\N{\fs90}Oh, it's like winning one of those things at the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.42,0:59:40.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我 我们至少有进度可言\N{\fs90}Thanks to me, at least,\N{\fs90}progress was being made.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.00,0:59:42.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,可是\N{\fs90}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.92,0:59:45.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我好像卡住了\N{\fs90}I'm stuck on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.56,0:59:51.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊哦 我弄坏了我的挖掘机\N{\fs90}Oh! Oh, I've broken\N{\fs90}my digger. Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.79,0:59:57.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我倒下了 詹姆斯则一事无成\N{\fs90}With me out of action\N{\fs90}and James achieving nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.80,0:59:59.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们需要一个新办法\N{\fs90}a new approach was needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.77,1:00:02.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是首先 我们要清场\N{\fs90}But first, we had to clear the site
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.19,1:00:04.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,清理杰里米的珍贵物品\N{\fs90}of Jeremy's most treasured possessions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.65,1:00:07.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,夏奇拉\N{\fs90}Shakira.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.92,1:00:09.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,夏奇拉\N{\fs90}Shakira.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.34,1:00:12.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,还是夏奇拉的\N{\fs90}Shakira.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.84,1:00:20.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,好刺眼!\N{\fs90}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.21,1:00:24.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,诅咒娃娃上有你的照片\N{\fs90}That is a... strong image.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.58,1:00:31.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 这儿有一本相册 可能很珍贵吧\N{\fs90}It's a tiny doll with pins\N{\fs90}in it, and your face.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.37,1:00:33.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,-但是有一点恼人\N{\fs90}Look, this is his photo album. \N{\fs90}It's probably really precious.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.00,1:00:34.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么\N{\fs90} -What?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.77,1:00:40.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-全都是我啊 -嗯哼\N{\fs90}-They're all of me. -Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.71,1:00:44.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,至此 我们决定不清场了\N{\fs90}At this point, we\N{\fs90}decided not to clear the site
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.77,1:00:46.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,让杰里米的东西随风去吧\N{\fs90}of his treasured possessions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.24,1:00:49.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,直接启动B计划\N{\fs90}and moved swiftly to plan B.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.58,1:00:51.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,简单说两句?\N{\fs90}Short ceremony,say a few words?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.90,1:00:53.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\fs90}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.53,1:01:14.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这\N{\fs90}- That...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.93,1:01:16.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-搞定了\N{\fs90}That got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.98,1:01:31.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 直说吧\N{\fs90}So, let's just get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.47,1:01:35.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们炸掉了我房子里的\N{\fs90}You blew up...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.68,1:01:37.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,那张骑马的画作?\N{\fs90}that picture of me on the horse?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.09,1:01:39.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 \N{\fs90}-Yep.-Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.50,1:01:44.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,伴随着我的失落 是时候结束了 感谢收看\N{\fs90}And on that terrible disappointment,\N{\fs90} it's time to end. Thanks for watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.63,1:01:46.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,下周见\N{\fs90}See you next week.
